             was indicted for <rs id="t17851019-79-off381" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17851019-79-off381" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17851019-79-off381" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               obtaining, on the <rs id="t17851019-79-cd382" type="crimeDate">8th day of May, 1784</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17851019-79-off381 t17851019-79-cd382"></join>, one hat, value 16 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17851019-79-victim842" type="victimName">
                           Richard 
                           Donn
                        <interp inst="t17851019-79-victim842" type="surname" value="Donn"></interp>
